@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }

        h1.display-4 {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        .card {
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .card-body {
            background: #ffffff;
        }

        ul.list-group-item {
            border: none;
        }

        ul.list-group-item::marker {
            color: #007bff;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="my-5 container">
        <h1 class="display-4 mb-4 text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

        <div class="card p-4 shadow-lg">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h2 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">Introduction</h2>
                <p class="lead">Welcome to our Privacy Policy page! Your privacy is important to us, and we want to make sure you understand how your personal information is handled. Please read the following policy to learn about how we collect, use, and protect your information.</p>

                <h2 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>We collect several types of information for various purposes to provide and improve our service to you. These include:</p>
                <ul class="list-group mb-4">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Personal Data (e.g., name, email address, etc.)</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Usage Data (e.g., how you use our website)</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Cookies and Tracking Data (e.g., how we track your activity on our website)</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use the collected information for various purposes:</p>
                <ul class="list-group mb-4">
                    <li class="list-group-item">To personalize your experience and respond to your requests</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">To improve and optimize our services</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">To send you promotional emails or newsletters (with your consent)</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">3. How We Protect Your Information</h2>
                <p>Your privacy is our priority. We take various security measures to ensure the protection of your personal data:</p>
                <ul class="list-group mb-4">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Encryption of sensitive information</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Secure servers and firewalls</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Access control to sensitive information</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">4. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
                <p>You have the following rights with respect to your personal data:</p>
                <ul class="list-group mb-4">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Right to access your data</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Right to correct or update your information</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Right to request deletion of your data</li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Right to object to the processing of your data</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">5. Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any significant changes by posting the updated policy on this page. Please review the policy periodically to stay informed about how we protect your data.</p>

                <h2 class="h4 mb-3 text-primary">6. Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, feel free to contact us:</p>
                <ul class="list-group mb-4">
                    <li class="list-group-item">Email: <strong>support@example.com</strong></li>
                    <li class="list-group-item">Phone: <strong>(123) 456-7890</strong></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
